           <h1 class="title" id="page-title">A Bustling-Personal Renegade against Fake Anonymity: Kiriti Sengupta’s <em>Selected Poems</em></h1>
      
          
    
          <div class="date-display-single">September 23, 2025</div>
    
          <div class="field-name-field-author field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix">
